How to put twitter bot on the Heroku server
    1. Things you need;
        1. git
        2. heroku login
    2. Process
        1. create Heroku app
        2. jump to the dir with cd command
        3. git init
        4. heroku git:remote -a __appName__ 
            - remote opperation, remote the app
        5. git add .
            - add all the changes to be ready
        6. commit 
        7. git push herou master 
            - done!!!
    3. Note
        1. You need to create a file called "Procfile" in the dir.
        2. Write "worker: node index.js" 
        3. Upload the changes and push to heroku server.
        